{"tid":211500,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"巴黎連番恐襲 65%前線警察支持瑪琳勒龐","createTime":"2017-04-21T16:17:07.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-22T07:05:49.000Z","uid":5195,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"fc81e51067abfaf09d29be284430b76f63235a1f","tid":211500,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T16:17:07.000Z","msg":"法國巴黎再次遭遇恐怖襲擊，當局認定是針對警方的行動。由於現正適逢總統選舉前夕，有分析認為恐襲或會將選民推向極右翼參選人瑪琳勒龐，令她有望登上總統寶座。<br />\n<br />\n國民陣線黨魁瑪琳勒龐於當地時間周四傍晚出席電視辯論時，提到法國所面臨的恐怖威脅，是長期寬鬆政策的惡果。話音剛落，當晚巴黎香榭麗舍大道便發生恐襲，瑪琳勒龐隨即亦在twitter上指又一個「噩夢」發生，並為警察所付出的沉重代價感到悲傷。<br />\n<br />\n不少分析均認為，如美國總統特朗普般宣揚嚴格移民政策的瑪琳勒龐，會因為本次恐襲得到更多選民支持。有形容國民陣線為「種族歧視黨派」的網民，亦不得不承認恐襲令瑪琳勒龐得益，更有人在恐襲後，標榜瑪琳勒龐為「法國最後的希望」。<br />\n<br />\n本周較早前亦有民調顯示，51%的法國警察選擇投票給瑪琳勒龐，遠遠拋離另外兩位候選人馬克宏和菲永分別獲得的16.5%及不到14%的支持度。在第一時間對應恐襲的前線部隊當中，瑪琳勒龐的支持度更高達65%，而在本次針對警方的恐襲後，她的支持度很有可能會再度急升。"},{"pid":"592f2ce0afd66cfbabc445b883d523adc4fa83d3","tid":211500,"uid":34348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T16:31:05.000Z","msg":"咁低？"},{"pid":"f4d81508d2eee6f5f2aed8270e272fc32d9b4aa0","tid":211500,"uid":55533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T16:35:53.000Z","msg":"你地冇做錯到！"},{"pid":"3c0bba2100c8fd8bc9ee095f8f9098019032c5ee","tid":211500,"uid":97814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-22T05:57:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b696c3dbe0bdf17a7d8d9d6d0f6f8ff4fab23315","tid":211500,"uid":13132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-22T06:03:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/22/140250_4c99a7340ca064fbcd452d3ebecb2b79.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F22%2F140250_4c99a7340ca064fbcd452d3ebecb2b79.jpg&h=663a5053&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nBin c<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a3a66d2b4c56f3df536f96662ab0a21d3d23e1f","tid":211500,"uid":71655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-22T06:05:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"48d130dc068fa4e6ee3bc5afe1089d9223826971","tid":211500,"uid":54228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-22T06:22:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/22/140250_4c99a7340ca064fbcd452d3ebecb2b79.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F22%2F140250_4c99a7340ca064fbcd452d3ebecb2b79.jpg&h=663a5053&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nBin c<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n企第一排唔知死剩幾多個</blockquote><br />\n最慘係呢班仆街唔死 死啲無辜嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"629512e2dde6a8c53674a26270f4d61ac686d7d3","tid":211500,"uid":20241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-22T06:25:24.000Z","msg":"點解d白鬼咁撚天真既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"040ffa72500ba91977f4c664f83c6d9777621a7d","tid":211500,"uid":35221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-22T06:29:00.000Z","msg":"咪發夢啦，法國始終左翼多"},{"pid":"611c0f9bb0e2eb795ff61df2bafdac34fd432f56","tid":211500,"uid":46328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-22T07:02:12.000Z","msg":"仲有人會信民調<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef3107eade4cf97309669644787c1bba3b80bb43","tid":211500,"uid":13132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-22T07:05:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/22/140250_4c99a7340ca064fbcd452d3ebecb2b79.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F22%2F140250_4c99a7340ca064fbcd452d3ebecb2b79.jpg&h=663a5053&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nBin c<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n企第一排唔知死剩幾多個</blockquote